	     <tr><td id=headerrow colspan=2 class=mform valign=top><a name=/db/item.html?item=12387&mid=102315572725312>&nbsp;</a><a id=sj href=/db/item.html?item=12387&mid=102315572725312>RE: Hmm... cool</a> <a id=fs8 href=/db/item.html?item=12387&mid=102315572725312#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a>
